{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-blog-post-tsx","path":"/markup-image-alignment","result":{"data":{"post":{"author":{"node":{"firstName":"Tyler","lastName":"Barnes","name":"tylbar","uri":"/author/tyler/","avatar":{"url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0a5bd2d18281009a03f01b8378abada1?s=96&d=mm&r=g"}}},"id":"cG9zdDoxMTc3","excerpt":"<p>Welcome to image alignment! The best way to demonstrate the ebb and flow of the various image positioning options is to nestle them snuggly among an ocean of words. Grab a paddle and let&#8217;s get started. On the topic of alignment, it should be noted that users can choose from the options of None, Left, [&hellip;]</p>\n","content":"<p>Welcome to image alignment! The best way to demonstrate the ebb and flow of the various image positioning options is to nestle them snuggly among an ocean of words. Grab a paddle and let&#8217;s get started.</p>\n<p>On the topic of alignment, it should be noted that users can choose from the options of <em>None</em>, <em>Left</em>, <em>Right, </em>and <em>Center</em>. In addition, they also get the options of <em>Thumbnail</em>, <em>Medium</em>, <em>Large</em> &amp; <em>Fullsize</em>. Be sure to try this page in RTL mode and it should look the same as LTR. </p>\n<p><span class=\"size-full wp-image-906 aligncenter inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:580px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:51.724137931034484%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/6549e/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 145w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/40fcf/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 290w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 580w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" srcSet=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/6549e/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 145w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/40fcf/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 290w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 580w\" src=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 580x300\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/6549e/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 145w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/40fcf/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 290w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 580w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" srcset=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/6549e/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 145w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/40fcf/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 290w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 580w\" src=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 580x300\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>The image above happens to be <em><strong>centered</strong></em>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"size-full wp-image-904 alignleft inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:150px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/82196/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 38w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/ab49a/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" srcSet=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/82196/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 38w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/ab49a/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 150w\" src=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 150x150\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/82196/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 38w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/ab49a/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" srcset=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/82196/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 38w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/ab49a/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 150w\" src=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 150x150\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span> The rest of this paragraph is filler for the sake of seeing the text wrap around the 150&#215;150 image, which is <em><strong>left aligned</strong></em>. </p>\n<p>As you can see the should be some space above, below, and to the right of the image. The text should not be creeping on the image. Creeping is just not right. Images need breathing room too. Let them speak like you words. Let them do their jobs without any hassle from the text. In about one more sentence here, we&#8217;ll see that the text moves from the right of the image down below the image in seamless transition. Again, letting the do it&#8217;s thang. Mission accomplished!</p>\n<p>And now for a <em><strong>massively large image</strong></em>. It also has <em><strong>no alignment</strong></em>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"alignnone  wp-image-907 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1200px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:33.333333333333336%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcSet=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 1200x400\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 1200x400\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>The image above, though 1200px wide, should not overflow the content area. It should remain contained with no visible disruption to the flow of content.</p>\n<p><span class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-907 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1200px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:33.333333333333336%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcSet=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 1200x400\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 1200x400\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>And we try the large image again, with the center alignment since that sometimes is a problem. The image above, though 1200px wide, should not overflow the content area. It should remain contained with no visible disruption to the flow of content.</p>\n<p><span class=\"size-full wp-image-905 alignright inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:300px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:66.66666666666667%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/ab49a/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/4934c/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 150w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcSet=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/ab49a/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/4934c/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 150w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 300w\" src=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 300x200\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/ab49a/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/4934c/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 150w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/ab49a/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/4934c/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 150w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 300w\" src=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 300x200\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></p>\n<p>And now we&#8217;re going to shift things to the <em><strong>right align</strong></em>. Again, there should be plenty of room above, below, and to the left of the image. Just look at him there&#8230; Hey guy! Way to rock that right side. I don&#8217;t care what the left aligned image says, you look great. Don&#8217;t let anyone else tell you differently.</p>\n<p>In just a bit here, you should see the text start to wrap below the right aligned image and settle in nicely. There should still be plenty of room and everything should be sitting pretty. Yeah&#8230; Just like that. It never felt so good to be right.</p>\n<p>And just when you thought we were done, we&#8217;re going to do them all over again with captions!</p>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_906\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-906\" style=\"width: 580px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><span class=\"size-full wp-image-906   inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:580px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:51.724137931034484%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/6549e/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 145w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/40fcf/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 290w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 580w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" srcSet=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/6549e/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 145w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/40fcf/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 290w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 580w\" src=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 580x300\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/6549e/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 145w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/40fcf/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 290w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 580w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" srcset=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/6549e/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 145w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/40fcf/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 290w,\n/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg 580w\" src=\"/static/539c0066996ddbcc605b6947b35b041e/c5338/image-alignment-580x300-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 580x300\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-906\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Look at 580&#215;300 getting some <a title=\"Image Settings\" href=\"https://en.support.wordpress.com/images/image-settings/\">caption</a> love.</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>The image above happens to be <em><strong>centered</strong></em>. The caption also has a link in it, just to see if it does anything funky.</p>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_904\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-904\" style=\"width: 150px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><span class=\"size-full wp-image-904   inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:150px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/82196/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 38w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/ab49a/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" srcSet=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/82196/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 38w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/ab49a/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 150w\" src=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 150x150\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/82196/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 38w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/ab49a/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" srcset=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/82196/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 38w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/ab49a/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg 150w\" src=\"/static/26a731845bd54a13d9e1ece5f47ec5b6/4934c/image-alignment-150x150-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 150x150\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-904\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bigger caption than the image usually is.</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>The rest of this paragraph is filler for the sake of seeing the text wrap around the 150&#215;150 image, which is <em><strong>left aligned</strong></em>. </p>\n<p>As you can see the should be some space above, below, and to the right of the image. The text should not be creeping on the image. Creeping is just not right. Images need breathing room too. Let them speak like you words. Let them do their jobs without any hassle from the text. In about one more sentence here, we&#8217;ll see that the text moves from the right of the image down below the image in seamless transition. Again, letting the do it&#8217;s thang. Mission accomplished!</p>\n<p>And now for a <em><strong>massively large image</strong></em>. It also has <em><strong>no alignment</strong></em>.</p>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_907\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-907\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><span class=\" wp-image-907 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1200px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:33.333333333333336%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcSet=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 1200x400\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" srcset=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/37e03/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 300w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/2a8be/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 600w,\n/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 1200x400\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-907\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Comment for massive image for your eyeballs.</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>The image above, though 1200px wide, should not overflow the content area. It should remain contained with no visible disruption to the flow of content.<br />\n<figure id=\"attachment_907\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-907\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\