027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/027d03300eb64c54a81adc70865e51f1/5a523/image-alignment-1200x4002-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 1200x400\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-907\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">This massive image is centered.</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>And again with the big image centered. The image above, though 1200px wide, should not overflow the content area. It should remain contained with no visible disruption to the flow of content.</p>\n<p><figure id=\"attachment_905\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-905\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><span class=\"size-full wp-image-905  inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:300px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:66.66666666666667%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/ab49a/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/4934c/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 150w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcSet=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/ab49a/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/4934c/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 150w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 300w\" src=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 300x200\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/ab49a/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/4934c/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 150w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/ab49a/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 75w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/4934c/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 150w,\n/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg 300w\" src=\"/static/60f9c6c7490bca0eecef9f0195a3b417/37e03/image-alignment-300x200-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image Alignment 300x200\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-905\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Feels good to be right all the time.</figcaption></figure></p>\n<p>And now we&#8217;re going to shift things to the <em><strong>right align</strong></em>. Again, there should be plenty of room above, below, and to the left of the image. Just look at him there&#8230; Hey guy! Way to rock that right side. I don&#8217;t care what the left aligned image says, you look great. Don&#8217;t let anyone else tell you differently.</p>\n<p>In just a bit here, you should see the text start to wrap below the right aligned image and settle in nicely. There should still be plenty of room and everything should be sitting pretty. Yeah&#8230; Just like that. It never felt so good to be right.</p>\n<p>And that&#8217;s a wrap, yo! You survived the tumultuous waters of alignment. Image alignment achievement unlocked! One last thing: The last item in this post&#8217;s content is a thumbnail floated right. Make sure any elements after the content are clearing properly.</p>\n<p><span class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-827 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:160px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:75%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/8d9e8/manhattansummer.jpg 40w,\n/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/e824a/manhattansummer.jpg 80w,\n/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/f7be0/manhattansummer.jpg 160w,\n/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/46946/manhattansummer.jpg 240w,\n/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/b4845/manhattansummer.jpg 320w,\n/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/bbe0c/manhattansummer.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 160px) 100vw, 160px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 160px) 100vw, 160px\" srcSet=\"/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/8d9e8/manhattansummer.jpg 40w,\n/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/e824a/manhattansummer.jpg 80w,\n/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/f7be0/manhattansummer.jpg 160w,\n/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/46946/manhattansummer.jpg 240w,\n/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/b4845/manhattansummer.jpg 320w,\n/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/bbe0c/manhattansummer.jpg 640w\" src=\"/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/f7be0/manhattansummer.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/9db2f95b5d9ff63178aec42c0ed47d1e/8d9e8/manhattansummer.jpg 40w,\n/static/9db2f95b5